=Analyze this Notion data containing {{ $json.projects.length }} projects and {{ $json.blocks.length }} blocks.

Extract text from blocks and match to projects using page IDs.

Make sure when deciding what are next steps for the project, determine this based on the latest updates for the project (found based on date within the project)

Projects data:
{{ JSON.stringify($json.projects) }}

Blocks data:
{{ JSON.stringify($json.blocks) }}


Today's date is: {{ $json.metadata.timestamp }}

